{"word":"H3359 - יְקַמְיָה - Yᵉqamyâh - yek-am-yaw' - Jekamiah","slug":"H3359","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יְקַמְיָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Yᵉqamyâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yek-am-yaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Jekamiah"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>יקמיה</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>yeqamyâh</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>yek-am-yaw'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Jecamiah or Jekamiah = \"Jehovah raises\" <ol><li>a descendant of Judah, son of Shallum in the line of Ahlai</li><li>a descendant of David and one of the seven introduced into the royal line on the failure of it in the person of Jehoiachin</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H6965\">H6965</a> and <a href=\"#/H3050\">H3050</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3351\">H3351</a>, <a href=\"#/H3356\">H3356</a>, <a href=\"#/H3360\">H3360</a>, <a href=\"#/H3361\">H3361</a>, <a href=\"#/H4725\">H4725</a>, <a href=\"#/H6965\">H6965</a>, <a href=\"#/H6967\">H6967</a>, <a href=\"#/H6968\">H6968</a>, <a href=\"#/H6970\">H6970</a>, <a href=\"#/H6971\">H6971</a>, <a href=\"#/H7009\">H7009</a>, <a href=\"#/H7012\">H7012</a>, <a href=\"#/H7054\">H7054</a>, <a href=\"#/H7056\">H7056</a>, <a href=\"#/H8617\">H8617</a>, <a href=\"#/H8618\">H8618</a>"}]}